SUMMARY:Winter Data & AI Meetup 2026 is coming!
DESCRIPTION:This February\, Data & Analytics Practice together with the Data Zen Community are excited to host the 4th Winter Data & AI Meetup — and this year\, AI takes center stage.\nFrom February 24 to 27\, we bring together data professionals\, analytics engineers and AI enthusiasts to share practical experience from real projects and discuss how data and AI are built\, governed and used in production.\nJOIN US!\n📅 Feb 24–27\n💻 Online\n🎟 Register per session4 \nAcross four days\, we’ll cover topics such as:\n• Modern data engineering and analytics platforms\n• AI-powered data governance and metadata management\n• Machine learning pipelines and production readiness\n• Data sharing\, data quality\, and scalable architectures\n• Real AI use cases from products and engineering teams\n• Technologies like Databricks\, BigQuery\, Microsoft Fabric and AI tooling\nYou can expect practical insights you can apply right after the meetup in a flexible online format with separate registration for each session.\nWho should attend?\nIntermediate to advanced level for professionals with hands-on experience: data engineers\, analytics professionals\, ML engineers\, AI practitioners\, and software engineers working with data and AI in real-world systems.\nJOIN THE SESSIONS!
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/winter-data-ai-meetup-2026-is-coming/
LOCATION:Online
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Facebook-post-8-2.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Community Day":MAILTO:community_day@wearecommunity.io
END:VEVENT
