SUMMARY:AI for Innovators Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:Join us for  good cheer and phenomenal conversations on  how AI is helping business owners\, entrepreneurs\, tech pros and the curious in North King/South Snohomish County. \nWhether you’re a founder\, a corporate innovator\, or simply curious about the local tech and business scene\, you’ll find good company here. Apple engineer or plumbing business owner…this means you! \n📍 Edway Taphouse\, Edmonds\n📅 Thurs.\, Feb. 26\n⏰ 4:30-7 PM \nAGENDA:\n4:30 PM – 5:00 PM: Open Networking and Grab a Drink\n5:00 PM – 6:00 PM: Guided Discussion\n– AI in daily operations (small business vs. enterprise)\n– Practical prompting: What works\, what doesn’t\, best vendors?\n– Sharing AI success stories or challenges across industries\n6:00 PM – 7 PM: Wrap-up Networking \nWHO THIS IS FOR:\n– Small business owners and entrepreneurs\n– Tech professionals\, contractors\, and startup founders\n– Anyone curious about applying AI to maximize their output \nWHAT YOU’LL WALK AWAY WITH:\n– How to incorporate AI into daily work—no matter your industry\n– How to assess AI tools and spot red flags\n– A network of fellow innovators using AI \nDrinks and connections await—RSVP now (attendance is FREE)! \nAdam & Ryan
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/ai-for-innovators-happy-hour/
LOCATION:EdWay Taphouse\, 22811 100th Ave W\, Edmonds\, 98020\, United States
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence,Meetups,Startups
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Feb-26-2.png
ORGANIZER;CN="North Sound Innovators":MAILTO:adam.peddicord@csbydesign.com
END:VEVENT
