SUMMARY:February Leadership Reset
DESCRIPTION:​A half-day reset for leaders who care deeply about their work and are feeling the strain of constant pressure\, context-switching\, and responsibility. \n​This live Seattle experience is designed for people leaders and senior individual contributors who want to lead\, think\, and decide with more clarity and steadiness\, without burning themselves out. \nNot a retreat from work. A reset for how you meet it. \nWe blend neuroscience\, breath\, movement\, and guided reflection to help you shift state\, regain focus\, and reconnect to your internal capacity in a way that fits real leadership life.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/february-leadership-reset/
LOCATION:Pioneer Collective – Belltown\, 92 Lenora St.\, Seattle\, 98121
CATEGORIES:Educational events,Science
