DESCRIPTION:ReedPop\, the world’s leading producer of pop culture events\, is returning to Seattle in March for Emerald City Comic Con (ECCC)\, taking place at the Seattle Convention Center. \nEmerald City Comic Con (ECCC) is the premier comic book and pop culture convention in the Pacific Northwest that celebrates comic books\, animation\, cartoons\, anime\, video games\, cosplay\, fantasy\, sci-fi\, pop culture\, and all things geek! \nECCC brings amazing guests for you to meet\, see in live panels\, and take photos with at the show!
