SUMMARY:Global Security Tour 2026 | Microsoft Keynote + Women in Tech | FREE
DESCRIPTION:Global Security Tour – Seattle 2026\nHosted by Seattle Data\, AI & Security \n📅 Saturday\, March 7th\, 2026\n🕘 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\n📍 Bellevue City Hall\n🎟️ RSVP: Free (Limited capacity)\n👥 500+ expected | Enterprise + Startup leaders in one room \nThe first Global Security Tour launches in Seattle — and it starts with a Microsoft executive keynote.\nIf you’re responsible for security outcomes\, budgets\, platforms\, or strategy\, this is the room you want to be in.\n✅ Keynote: Corporate Vice President (Microsoft) – Sentinel Data Lake\n✅ Microsoft product leaders attending across Security Copilot\, Microsoft Sentinel\, Defender\, and Purview\n✅ Women in Tech panel featuring senior voices and real career leadership stories\n✅ Hackathon experience (build / learn / collaborate — details coming soon)\n✅ High-value networking with senior enterprise leaders\, founders\, and builders \nWhy Directors & VPs are showing up \nSee where unified security operations is going — straight from the leaders building it\nGet practical direction on how enterprises are approaching modern SecOps (without the salesy fluff)\nMeet peers facing the same challenges: scale\, visibility\, governance\, SOC efficiency\, and AI adoption\nBuild relationships that matter — Microsoft leaders\, enterprise decision-makers\, and startups solving real problems\nWhat to expect (speaker roster + detailed agenda coming soon) \nMicrosoft executive keynote\nLeadership sessions + discussions (Sentinel / Defender / Purview / Security Copilot ecosystem)\nWomen in Tech panel\nNetworking blocks built for meaningful conversations\nPerks \nFree registration (limited seats)\nBreakfast + lunch + coffee included\nSwag\, giveaways & strong networking energy\nThis isn’t just another security event — it’s the start of a tour and a community movement.\nIf you want early access to the conversations shaping security platforms and AI-powered SecOps\, register now. \n👉 RSVP (Free) — reserve your seat before it fills.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/global-security-tour-2026-microsoft-keynote-women-in-tech-free/
LOCATION:Bellevue City Hall\, 450 110th Ave NE\, Bellevue\, WA\, 98004\, United States
CATEGORIES:Artificial Intelligence
