SUMMARY:Seattle Tech Week
DESCRIPTION:Seattle Tech Week 2026 dates are live — mark your calendar! \n📅 July 27–31 📅 \nFor the fourth year in a row\, we’re bringing together the builders\, operators\, investors\, and leaders who make Seattle one of the world’s most dynamic tech ecosystems. \nFor the uninitiated: Seattle Tech Week turns the entire city into a giant\, open-source conference. It’s not about one stage or venue. It’s nearly 200 events hosted by the people actually building the future: founders\, operators\, VCs\, and community leaders. You’ll find real conversations\, magnetic ideas\, and connections that go far deeper than your typical conference business card swap. \nSeattle Tech Week is truly about connecting\, learning\, and celebrating the talent and innovation that define our community. Whether you’re a founder\, operator\, investor\, or just passionate about tech\, there’s something here for you. \nImportant dates:\n📅 April 9: Event submissions open\n📅 May 14: STW calendar of events goes live\n📅 June 25: Event Attendee Registration opens\n📅 July 27: Seattle Tech Week begins \nInterested in hosting an event during 2026 STW and never have → email: techweek@madrona.com for more information.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/seattle-tech-week/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-08-121154.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Madrona Venture Group":MAILTO:sudip@madrona.com
END:VEVENT
